53:29.858 --> 53:35.595
<i>♪ You'd have me down, down
Down, down on my knees ♪</i>

53:35.597 --> 53:36.995
<i>♪ Now, wouldn't ya ♪</i>

53:36.997 --> 53:38.599
<i>♪ Barracuda ♪</i>

53:39.633 --> 53:41.700
