53:41.702 --> 53:43.405
[whispers]
It's okay, honey, you...

53:44.405 --> 53:46.072
Hey. Excuse me.

53:46.074 --> 53:48.407
Sir?

53:48.409 --> 53:50.411
Excuse me.
Sir, can I...

53:51.880 --> 53:53.613
Can I just talk...

53:53.615 --> 53:56.081
Can I just... Can I talk
to you for a second?

53:56.083 --> 53:58.684
