About my score?

53:58.686 --> 53:59.921
Happy to.

54:07.128 --> 54:10.365
I know that you guys
don't... like me.

54:11.800 --> 54:15.668
But... I'm landing
all my jumps out there.

54:15.670 --> 54:16.905
Tonya.

54:18.606 --> 54:20.642
It's never been entirely
about the skating.

54:22.776 --> 54:26.077
I'll deny I ever said it,
honey, but you're just not...

54:26.079 --> 54:28.750
the image
that we want to portray.

54:30.017 --> 54:32.718
You're representing our country,
for fuck's sake.

54:32.720 --> 54:35.454
We need to see
a wholesome American family,

54:35.456 --> 54:36.758
and you...

54:39.526 --> 54:41.463
you just refuse
to play along.

54:44.532 --> 54:47.001
I don't have
a wholesome American family.

54:49.871 --> 54:52.673
Why... Why can't it just be
about the skating?

54:56.677 --> 54:59.077
[Tonya] <i>They want a
wholesome American family?</i>

54:59.079 --> 55:00.512
Fuck you.
Give me that.

55:00.514 --> 55:04.952
<i>Well, it's not gonna be easy, but,
yeah, I could pull that out of my ass.</i>

55:10.224 --> 55:12.427
Shit.

55:14.061 --> 55:16.262
[sighs]

55:16.264 --> 55:18.901
