bucks back. They didn't do anything.

01:04:35.688 --> 01:04:38.689
Your thousand bucks?
Jeff, come on.

01:04:38.691 --> 01:04:42.693
Are... Tonya. You still
want this to happen, right?

01:04:42.695 --> 01:04:46.097
