- I really don't care, Shawn.

01:04:46.099 --> 01:04:48.268
I clearly have
bigger shit to fry.

01:04:48.802 --> 01:04:50.471
You eat shit?

01:04:52.206 --> 01:04:55.173
- What?
- "Fish to fry," not "shit to fry."

01:04:55.175 --> 01:04:58.610
