back, and has never been laid.

01:05:16.630 --> 01:05:19.398
Just stay away from me!

01:05:19.400 --> 01:05:22.700
- January 6.
- I had a session later that night so...

01:05:22.702 --> 01:05:24.572
- I was sleeping, yeah.
- I was asleep.

01:05:34.581 --> 01:05:37.849
Remember, if your mind is blank,
no one can pick up your vibes.

01:05:37.851 --> 01:05:41.188
Also, they can't identify you
if they don't see your eyes.

01:05:42.456 --> 01:05:43.456
Go.

01:06:02.876 --> 01:06:04.344
Mind's blank.

01:06:05.378 --> 01:06:07.214
Don't let them see my eyes.

01:06:23.530 --> 01:06:24.530
The john?

01:06:50.523 --> 01:06:53.694
Hey. Hey.
Which one's Kerrigan?

01:07:26.793 --> 01:07:28.195
[screams]

01:07:29.329 --> 01:07:31.766
[Nancy screaming]

01:07:51.851 --> 01:07:53.220
What the fuck?

01:07:56.623 --> 01:07:57.658
[engine starts]

01:07:59.592 --> 01:08:00.595
[grunts]

01:08:08.735 --> 01:08:11.338
Go! Go, go, go, go,
go, go, go, go, go!

01:08:13.274 --> 01:08:16.875
I mean, we had no idea that
something like this could be done

01:08:16.877 --> 01:08:18.943
by two of the biggest boobs,

01:08:18.944 --> 01:08:23.682
in a story
populated solely by boobs.

01:08:23.684 --> 01:08:24.782
[laughs]

01:08:24.783 --> 01:08:26.487
[phone rings]

01:08:30.024 --> 01:08:30.921
- Yeah?
- [Tonya] <i>Jeff?</i>

01:08:30.923 --> 01:08:32.624
